Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Naut and Rossi should be fine.}{\i0}Naut và Rossi sẽ ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{R-Right.}{\i0}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sure they are...}{\i0}Nhất định là thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise was...}{\i0}Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{planning to do that from the start.}{\i0}ngay từ đầu đã định làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She knew she had no hope of surviving.}{\i0}Cô ấy biết mình đã hết hi vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even so, she tried to be useful to us.}{\i0}Dù vậy nhưng vẫn cố gắng giúp chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But if only I'd been paying\Ncloser attention to her...}{\i0}Nhưng nếu tôi chịu chú ý đến cô ấy hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're wrong about that.}{\i0}Không phải thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise died because I let my guard down.}{\i0}Blaise chết vì tôi đã bất cẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That can't be!}{\i0}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, I'm not making the same mistake again.}{\i0}Thế nên để không phạm phải sai lầm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm taking you to the royal capital,\Nwhatever it takes!}{\i0}Tôi sẽ đưa Jess đến thủ đô bằng mọi giá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's...}{\i0}Nhất định...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{enter the royal capital together,\Nno matter what.}{\i0}cả hai hãy cùng đến được thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's something\NI want you to promise me.}{\i0}Có chuyện tôi muốn Jess hứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What is it?}{\i0}Là gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Being a pig, I wouldn't be allowed\Nto enter the royal capital without you.}{\i0}Là một con heo, tôi sẽ không được \Nvào thủ đô nếu không có cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But you should be able\Nto get in on your own.}{\i0}Nhưng một mình Jess thì có thể vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If anything happens to me, you keep\Nheading straight for the royal capital.}{\i0}Nếu tôi có mệnh hệ gì thì \Nphải chạy thật nhanh vào thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Got that?}{\i0}Hiểu chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig...}Anh heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Without you, I...}{\i0}Không có anh tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{just can't...}{\i0}nếu không có anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We've been putting our lives on the line\Nto get you safely to the royal capital!}{\i0}Chúng ta đã đặt cược mạng \Nsống để Jess đến được thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's your duty to live up to that!}{\i0}Nên nghĩa vụ của cô là phải sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, I want you to have the resolve\Nto reach the royal capital, no matter what!}{\i0}Thế nên phải bằng mọi giá đến được thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù cho...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,có một mình đi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right.}{\i0}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}{There's Always a Reason\NWhy Things Are the Way They Are}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If we were to run into any Yethma hunters...}{\i0}Nếu đụng phải thợ săn Yethma lúc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the only things I could use...}{\i0}thứ duy nhất mình có thể dùng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{are these anklets, and...}{\i0}là chiếc vòng này và...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can activate all three of them\Nby pulling those pins and snapping them.}{\i0}Cô có thể kích hoạt nó bằng cách kéo chốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The one with the red rista\Nembedded in it is a bomb.}{\i0}Rista đỏ là một quả bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It doesn't have the widest range,\Nbut it's potent enough.}{\i0}Phạm vi không rộng nhưng đủ mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The yellow one is a sielter.}{\i0}Quả màu vào là sielter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Use it when you want to hide.}{\i0}Dùng nó để trốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It'll look like a rock.}{\i0}Nó sẽ nguỵ trang thành tảng đá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The green one is a wolf call\Nthat summons wolves inaudibly to humans.}{\i0}Màu xanh lá là triệu hồi những con sói.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Activate it, and some irritable wolves\Nwill show up.}{\i0}Kích hoạt nó và lũ sói sẽ xuất hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How long before the wolves get here?}{\i0}Mất bao lâu để lũ sói đến?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't know.}{\i0}Không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But here in the Needle Woods,\Nthere's no way that they wouldn't show up.}{\i0}Nhưng ở khu rừng kim này, \Nchắc chắn chúng sẽ xuất hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can use the sielter to hide.}{\i0}Và dùng sielter để trốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you're lucky, the wolves\Nwill chase off the Yethma hunters.}{\i0}Nếu may mắn, lũ sói sẽ đuổi đám thợ săn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{At least, they might.}{\i0}Hi vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not the most user-friendly tools, are they?}{\i0}Là thứ khó dùng nhất à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ideally, you wouldn't have to use them at all.}{\i0}Lý tưởng nhất là không dùng đến nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But if it ever comes to it...}{\i0}Nhưng nếu bất trắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{think hard before you use them.}{\i0}hãy suy nghĩ kĩ trước khi dùng đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is it.}{\i0}Đây à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{The entrance...}{\i0}Lối vào...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Where do you think it is?}{\i0}Ở đâu được nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Blaise said to appeal to the king.}{\i0}Blaise nói hãy quỳ xuống trước đức vua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Luckily, there don't seem to be\Nany Yethma hunters nearby.}{\i0}May là quanh đây không có thợ săn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Jess, it probably won't work,}{\i0}Jess, có thể nó sẽ không có tác dụng,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{but try shouting the words\N"Please let me in" toward the cliff.}{\i0}nhưng thử hướng về tảng đá và \Nnói "Hãy cho chúng tôi vào" xem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If it doesn't work,\Nwe'll move on right away.}{\i0}Nếu không được thì tìm cách khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please let me in!}Hãy cho tôi vào!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{It looks like I was wrong.}{\i0}Có vẻ không đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Oh, well. Let's go.}{\i0}Chịu thôi, đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Right.}{\i0}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please let me in!}Hãy cho tôi vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{No good yet again, huh?}{\i0}Vẫn không được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Let's go.}{\i0}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Where the heck...}{\i0}Rốt cuộc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{is that entrance?}{\i0}Lối vào ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How about riding me again?}{\i0}Leo lên tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can still walk.}Tôi vẫn có thể đi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not only don't we have a clue\Nwhere the entrance is,}{\i0}Chúng ta chẳng có manh mối gì về lối vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{we also don't know\Nwhen we'll come under attack again.}{\i0}Và cũng không biết lúc nào sẽ bị tấn công.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We're going to need some stamina\Nif that happens, right?}{\i0}Nên cần phải nghỉ ngơi để dành sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, come on, get on me.}{\i0}Nên là leo lên đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig...}Anh heo....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's talk about something.}Chúng ta nói chuyện gì đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah, let's do that.}{\i0}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, tell me about your\Nfirst love, Mister Pig.}Vậy kể về tình đầu của anh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It looks like someone's there.}{\i0}Có ai đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Young lady!}Tiểu thư à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No use trying to escape!}Bỏ chạy vô ích.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just come out here like a good girl!}Ngoan ngoãn ra đây nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't move, Jess!\NIs that wound deep?}{\i0}Đừng di chuyển Jess! Vết thương có sâu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No.}{\i0}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm all right.}{\i0}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that guy alone?}{\i0}Tên đó đi một mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How can I give Jess a chance to escape?}{\i0}Làm sao để Jess trốn được đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Compose yourself and think!}{\i0}Suy nghĩ đi tôi ơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Excuse me...}{\i0}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but I'm okay.}{\i0}tôi vẫn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please run, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Nên anh heo hãy chạy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't be ridiculous!}{\i0}Đừng có nói ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This time, I'm gonna protect you!}{\i0}Lần này tôi sẽ bảo vệ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I...}{\i0}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{really enjoyed myself.}{\i0}thực sự đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So...}{\i0}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no way I'd abandon you, Jess!}{\i0}Tôi sẽ không bỏ rơi cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not in a million years!}{\i0}Không bao giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Whatever you do...}{\i0}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{don't sound like you've given up!}{\i0}đừng có từ bỏ lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is someone else there?}Có ai ở đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whisper all you want,\Nbut it's not gonna get you anywhere!}Đừng có thì thầm nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{See, that arrow...}Mũi tên đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've applied poison to it!}có độc đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're not going to survive!}Ngươi sẽ chết chắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu có đồng bọn thì ta sẽ tha cho hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no scent of poison.}{\i0}Không có mùi độc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's bluffing!}{\i0}Hắn đang nói dối.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's just checking to see\Nif any allies are lurking around!}{\i0}Hắn chỉ đang kiểm tra xem\N chúng ta có đồng bọn không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't you answer him!}{\i0}Đừng đáp lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm only after you, young lady!}Ta chỉ nhắm vào tiểu thư đó thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm coming over...}Ta sẽ đến đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{all right?}được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No good, huh?}{\i0}Không được à.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're up to something, aren't you?}Này, ngươi định làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Not good.}Không tốt đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm on my own,\Nso I can't have you resisting me.}Ta đi có một mình thôi, \Nkhông cần phải chống cự.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, he's got no reason to hurry\Nwhen he's up against a wounded Yethma.}{\i0}Hắn không cần vội vã khi đấu với một Yethma yếu đuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Dammit! So, there's another one!}{\i0}Mẹ nó! Quả nhiên có 2 tên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, give me the red ball.}{\i0}Jess, đưa tôi viên màu đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's another enemy in hiding!}{\i0}Vẫn còn một kẻ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But they're still wary of us\Npossibly having more allies on our side!}{\i0}Nhưng chúng vẫn đang cảnh giác chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's use that against them!}{\i0}Hãy phản công!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Start off by calling out\Nas if a friend's nearby!}{\i0}Đầu tiên gọi đồng minh ở gần!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut, no!}Anh Naut, đừng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You mustn't come here!}Đừng đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right! Activate the wolf call!}{\i0}Rồi! Kích hoạt quả gọi sói đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I knew there was someone nearby.}Biết ngay là có kẻ nào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All that whispering\Nmade me suspect as much.}Ta đã nghi ngờ khi nghe những lời thì thầm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ugh!}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Can you believe that sound?}{\i0}Cái âm thanh gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Pig?}{\i0}Anh heo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm fine.}{\i0}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{R-Right.}{\i0}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's no use! Naut or whatever...}Vô ích thôi, Naut hay ai đi nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{there's no saving that Yethma!}không cần phải cứu Yethma đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The poison's circulating\Nthroughout her body even as we speak!}Chất độc đang ngấm vào cô ta\N ngay cả khi ta đang nói chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to create a diversion!}{\i0}Tôi sẽ đánh lạc hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, you take advantage\Nand run as far away as you can!}{\i0}Jess lợi dụng điều đó và chạy đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But what about you, Mister Pig?}{\i0}Nhưng còn anh heo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't worry! I'll be right behind you.}{\i0}Đừng lo, tôi chạy ngay phía sau!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, crap—}{\i0}Chết tiệt--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the hell? A boar?}Gì chứ? Lợn rừng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Will that do?}{\i0}Liệu nó có tác dụng?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, do you think you can retreat?}{\i0}Jess, rút lui được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes!}{\i0}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Somehow.}{\i0}Có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay!}{\i0}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Keep moving as far away as you can\Nand hide in the sielter!}{\i0}Tiếp tục chạy càng xa càng tốt và sử dụng sielter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What was that?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We're splitting up!}Chúng ta phải tách nhau ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Gotcha!}Hiểu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There, huh?}Ở đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just come on out!}Ra đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've got to hold him off\Nso Jess can run away.}{\i0}Phải câu giờ cho Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{These nuts are...}{\i0}Hạt này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come out right now!}Mau ra đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna get rough with you!}Đừng để ta mạnh tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Like I'd fall for that.}{\i0}Còn lâu ta mới bị dụ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? What is this?}Gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sure I will!}{\i0}Thích thì chiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey! What's wrong?}Này! Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Where the hell are you hiding?}Ngươi trốn đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're all right?}Này, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Pig!}{\i0}Anh Heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please save me!}{\i0}Hãy cứu tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't tell me there's another Yethma hunter!}{\i0}Lại thêm một thợ săn Yethma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, where are you?}{\i0}Jess, cô đâu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey...}{\i0}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No way!}{\i0}Đùa nhau sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please...}{\i0}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hãy ở yên đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You dummy!}{\i0}Con ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now I can't distract the enemy!}{\i0}Thế này sao tôi đánh lạc hướng chúng được?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What if they find you?}{\i0}Chúng tìm ra thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're the dummy, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Người ngốc là anh đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If I'd gone into the sielter alone...}{\i0}Nếu tôi sử dụng sielter một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{what were you going to do\Nwhen the wolves showed up?}{\i0}thì anh sẽ làm gì khi đám sói xuất hiện?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What would I do? Of course I'd...}{\i0}Làm gì á?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, get up! Wolves!}Này tỉnh lại mau! Lũ sói đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Run!}Chạy mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{See? If you'd been outside,\Njust think what would've become of you.}{\i0}Đấy, nếu anh ở bên ngoài thì sẽ ra sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's true. I owe you one.}{\i0}Đúng thật, nợ cô rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But that's just hindsight!}{\i0}Nhưng giờ vẫn còn sớm để mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We're still in danger, you know!}{\i0}Chúng ta vẫn đang nguy hiểm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Who knows when the wolves might come back?}{\i0}Ai mà biết lũ sói có quay lại không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It would've been safer for me\Nto distract those men and the wolves!}{\i0}Đáng ra tôi nên đánh lạc hướng lũ thợ săn và đám sói.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It would be pointless for me\Nto be the only one to survive.}{\i0}Chỉ có tôi sống sót thì có nghĩa lí gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It has to be you and me, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Phải là hai chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How many times do I have to tell you?}{\i0}Tôi đã dặn bao nhiêu lần rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Look, Jess, the truth is,\Nyou don't want to die, right?}{\i0}Jess, cô không muốn chết, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, look out for yourself better!}{\i0}Nên là hãy quan tâm đến bản thân đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's all right for you to be more selfish!}{\i0}Cô cứ tỏ ra ích kỷ cũng được!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I've already been selfish enough.}{\i0}Tôi ích kỷ đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{That's not true!}{\i0}Không đúng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{When have you ever been\Nthe least bit selfish?}{\i0}Lần cuối cô ích kỷ là khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{By not wanting you to ever die, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Là không muốn anh chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't even stroke your head...}{\i0}Quả nhiên cái chân này...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{with these pig feet after all.}{\i0}sao có thể xoa đầu cô được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm happy enough\Njust knowing you feel that way.}{\i0}Chỉ cần cảm xúc của anh là đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't read my mind!}{\i0}Đừng có đọc suy nghĩ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sorry.}{\i0}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think it's safe for us to come out.}{\i0}Có vẻ an toàn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you okay?}{\i0}Cô ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes, more or less.}{\i0}Vâng, có vẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How about you, Mister Pig?}{\i0}Còn anh heo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah.}{\i0}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm much better now.}{\i0}Tôi ổn hơn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's go.}{\i0}Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um, Mister Pig...}Anh heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've never had someone\Nstay so close to me before.}Tôi chưa từng được gần gũi với ai như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Stop. Don't put up any death flags.}{\i0}Này, đừng có dựng deathflag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was truly happy.}Tôi đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I just wanted to let you know that.}Chỉ muốn nói cho anh nghe điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you all right?}{\i0}Cô ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's take a break here for now.}{\i0}Hãy ra kia nghỉ một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no end to this.}{\i0}Mãi mà không kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig, are you happy right now?}Anh heo có đang hạnh phúc không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No.}{\i0}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I wouldn't call myself happy.}{\i0}Hạnh phúc cái gì chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Because I still don't think\NI've truly made you happy yet.}{\i0}Vì tôi vẫn chưa làm cho Jess hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh no, I...}Không đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well, but even if I were to die right now,\NI wouldn't have any regrets.}{\i0}Cơ mà dù giờ có chết thì tôi cũng không hối hận.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Having a beautiful young girl\Npress her breasts against me...}{\i0}Được áp mặt vào ngực gái xinh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's something I never would've experienced\Nleading a normal life!}{\i0}Là kinh nghiệm tôi chưa từng trải ở thế giới cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, being a pig isn't all bad!}{\i0}Thế nên làm heo cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If that's all you need...}Nếu anh muốn thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hold up, that was a virgin joke.}{\i0}Khoan, là cuồng dâm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If...}Nếu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you were reincarnated,\Nwhat would you want to be?}Nếu được tái sinh, anh muốn trở thành gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well, a human.}{\i0}Con người...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But other than that, maybe a dog.}{\i0}Nhưng nếu là thú thì chó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Getting all that praise\Njust for fetching a ball! I'm a little envious.}{\i0}Được khen chỉ vì bắt trúng bóng làm tôi ghen tị.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What a funny reason that is!}Cái lý do mắc cười ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What do you want to be, Jess?}{\i0}Thế còn Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's see.}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I guess maybe a pig.}Có lẽ là heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Does even Jess have a unique fetish\Nthat makes her long to be called a "sow"?}{\i0}Jess có sở thích làm một con heo cái à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh no, I don't mean it that way.}Ý tôi không phải theo nghĩa đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you don't manage to turn\Nback into a human, Mister Pig...}Nếu anh không thể thành người...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{then...}thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig, there's something\NI have to tell you.}Anh Heo, có chuyện tôi phải nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Heckripon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're sure they're harmless?}{\i0}Chúng thực sự vô hại nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Heckripons don't do anything.}Heckripon sẽ không làm gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They're weird creatures for sure.}{\i0}Chúng đúng là sinh vật kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We didn't have them where I come from—}{\i0}Ở thế giới của tôi làm gì có--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm told that they suddenly\Nincreased their numbers...}{\i0}Đột nhiên chúng tăng số lượng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{after the end of the dark ages.}{\i0}sau khi thời kì hắc ám biến mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{They only bring misfortune.}{\i0}Chúng chỉ mang đến vận xui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Although it's only been in the last few years\Nthat people started saying that.}{\i0}Vài năm gần đây mới có tin đồn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Did a bunch of heckripons gather\Nor something before that incident?}{\i0}Chẳng phải trước khi xảy ra vụ tai nạn đó thì\N có nhiều Heckripon đã tập trung lại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{There are two laws concerning Yethmas.}{\i0}Có hai luật lệ liên quan đến Yethma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Appeal to the king.}{\i0}Cúi đầu trước nhà vua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess...}{\i0}Này Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{so you really believe\Nthat heckripons don't do anything?}{\i0}cô thực sự tin rằng Heckripon không làm gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But the truth is...}{\i0}Nhưng sự thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{heckripons are doing a certain thing.}{\i0}heckripon làm một chuyện rõ ràng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think that one must be watching us.}{\i0}Là chúng đang quan sát chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, I agree, but...}Chuyện đó đúng là thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Listen, Jess.}{\i0}Nghe này Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The animals here in Mesteria\Nalso exist in the world I come from.}{\i0}Những động vật ở đây thì ở thế giới tôi cũng có.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The only exception being heckripons.}{\i0}Thứ duy nhất không có là heckripon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Living creatures interact\Nin complex ways to survive.}{\i0}Các sinh vật sống tương tác \Ntheo nhiều cách để tồn tại.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The ecosystem is built\Non that delicate balance.}{\i0}Hệ sinh thái được xây dựng dựa trên sự cân bằng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Having an oddball creature like that\Nin the mix just doesn't make sense.}{\i0}Tự nhiên có một sinh vật kì quặc này thật khó hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Which leads me to speculate...}{\i0}Nó làm tôi suy đoán...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{that heckripons were actually brought in\Nfrom outside the ecosystem around the dark ages.}{\i0}những con heckripon này đã được đưa ra\N ngoài hệ sinh thái trong thời kì hắc ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That they were created by a mage.}{\i0}Chúng được các ma thuật sư tạo ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But for what reason?}Nhưng tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In order to see.}{\i0}Để quan sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Meaning, for surveillance.}{\i0}Tức là giám sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Some time before the convent\Nat Baptsaze burned down,}{\i0}Một khoảng thời gian trước khi\N Baptsaze bị thiêu cháy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{there was a surge in heckripons in the\Nsurrounding area. That's what Ceres told us.}{\i0}số lượng Heckripon đã\N gia tăng xung quanh khu vực.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't you think it's weird that a stone building\Ncould be burned into nothingness?}{\i0}Cô có thấy lạ khi một toà nhà \Nbằng đá bị thiêu rụi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But if a mage watching through the eyes\Nof the heckripons did it}{\i0}Nhưng nếu có ma thuật sư\N nào đó thông qua Heckripon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{to punish people for hiding Yethmas,\Nthen yeah, that makes sense!}{\i0}trừng phạt những Yethma ở đó thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why would they do that?}Tại sao lại làm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở đất nước này, điều luật bị cấm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,là vận chuyển và lạm dụng\N tình dục Yethma, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't that because they're afraid that some Yethmas\Nmight escape surveillance or increase in number?}{\i0}Đó không phải là do họ sợ rằng những Yethma\N sẽ trốn thoát và gia tăng số lượng sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They need Yethmas\Nto either reach the royal capital...}{\i0}Họ cần Yethma đến thủ đô...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{or else die when they turn 16.}{\i0}nếu không sẽ chết khi qua tuổi 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's why they created this system!\NI can't think of any other reason!}{\i0}Đó là lý do họ tạo nên hệ thống này!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But we haven't done anything wrong!}Nhưng bọn tôi không làm gì sai cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's ask them why directly...}{\i0}Hãy hỏi trực tiếp đức vua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{in the royal capital!}{\i0}Ở thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you ready, Jess?}{\i0}Sẵn sàng chưa Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please let me enter the royal capital!}Hãy cho tôi vào thủ đô!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd like to talk to you\Nabout what a Yethma really is!}Tôi muốn hỏi về Yethma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No good, huh?}{\i0}Không được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's go!}{\i0}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
